TITLE: Implementing Inline Theme Script for Dark Mode in Astro
DESCRIPTION: This script maintains dark mode preference in localStorage and prevents Flash of Unstyled Content (FOUC). It initializes the theme based on user preference or system settings and sets up a MutationObserver to track changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/huntabyte/shadcn-svelte/blob/main/sites/docs/src/content/dark-mode/astro.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: astro
CODE:
```
<script is:inline>
  const isBrowser = typeof localStorage !== 'undefined';
  const getThemePreference = () => {
    if (isBrowser && localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
      return localStorage.getItem('theme');
    }
    return window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches
      ? 'dark' : 'light';
  };
  const isDark = getThemePreference() === 'dark';
  document.documentElement.classList[isDark ? 'add' : 'remove']('dark');

  if (isBrowser) {
    const observer = new MutationObserver(() => {
      const isDark = document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark');
      localStorage.setItem('theme', isDark ? 'dark' : 'light');
    });
    observer.observe(document.documentElement, {
      attributes: true,
      attributeFilter: ['class']
    });
  }
</script>

<html lang="en">
	<body>
      <h1>Astro</h1>
	</body>
</html>
</script>
```

