TITLE: Updating AlertDialog Component with flyAndScale Transition in Svelte
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to update a Svelte component to use the new flyAndScale transition. It removes the animation classes previously used with tailwindcss-animate and adds transition props that use the flyAndScale function from utils.js.
SOURCE: https://github.com/huntabyte/shadcn-svelte/blob/main/sites/docs/src/content/changelog.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: svelte
